Subject: [PATCH 5.15 078/279] powerpc/dcr: Use cmplwi instead of 3-argument cmpli
Date:   Wed, 24 Nov 2021 12:56:05 +0100
Message-Id: <20211124115721.408342386@linuxfoundation.org>
